descriptionHtml:
Break undies (linked health)

[b]Require:[/b]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17542]Qasmoke Door[/url]

[b]Installation:[/b]
Unpack the contents to your Skyrim data folder.

[b]Location:[/b]
Qasmoke(testing hall)
1 - [coc qasmoke] in the console.
2 - Buy it by merchant
3 - [coc Riverwood] in the console.
